snippet.title: Amber Heard Reportedly Still Getting offers in Hollywood Despite all Controversy
snippet.description:
Despite all the controversies Amber Heard reportedly is still getting offers from Hollywood. Watch this video till the end to know if it's true or it's just a rumor. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI

Johnny Depp reportedly wanted to have his ex-wife Amber Heard replaced in Aquaman, according to recent reports by The Hollywood Reporter. But despite all the controversies Amber Heard reportedly is still getting offers from Hollywood. Watch this video till the end to know if it's true or it's just a rumor.
